      "role": "user",
      "content": "idk i just dont like the idea of taking them for 10 days if the symptoms are 100% gone. it feels like overkill. what if i just take a probiotic every day to balance out the gut stuff and then stop the antibiotics now? wouldn't that basically solve the problem without me having to take the rest of the pills? it seems much more efficient to just focus on the gut health part since the infection is already visually gone.",
